| Caller     | Callee  | Relationship | Reason |
|------------|---------|--------------|----------------------------------------------|
| **User**   | Auction | ✘            | User is a base module; it does not manage auctions |
| **User**   | Bid     | ✘            | User does not initiate bidding logic         |
| **User**   | Item    | ✘            | User only provides seller/buyer identity     |
|            |         |              |                                              |
| **Bid**    | User    | ✔︎           | Needs buyer information (user_id) when placing bids |
| **Bid**    | Auction | ✔︎           | Validates auction status, rules, end time, and reserve price |
| **Bid**    | Item    | ✘            | Bid does not access or modify item details   |
|            |         |              |                                              |
| Bid (view) | User    | Read-only    | When displaying bid history, needs buyer username |
| Bid (view) | Auction | Read-only    | Displays highest bid and bidding history     |
|            |         |              |                                              |
| **Others** | User    | ✔︎ (Read)     | Other modules need basic user info (seller / buyer) |
